Velocity of Detonation (VoD) is the velocity at which the shock wave travels through an explosive charge upon detonation.  The ShotTrack VoD 305 is the next-generation VoD monitor, designed and manufactured for ease of use, refined performance and reliability. Its features include: The ShotTrack VoD 305 is available right now and will soon be accompanied by the ShotTrack ViB and ShotTrack BiC, two other products that adhere to ShotTrack’s dedication to design, development and manufacture of state of the art electronic monitoring equipment for the use in mining and construction industries.